#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn35.69"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn35.69:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.69:0.2"
msgid "7. Migajālavagga "
msgstr "7. With Migajāla "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 69. Upasenaāsīvisasutta → upasenasuttaṃ (bj) | upasena (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.69:0.3"
msgid "69. Upasenaāsīvisasutta "
msgstr "69. Upasena and the Viper "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn35.69:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā ca sāriputto āyasmā ca upaseno rājagahe viharanti sītavane sappasoṇḍikapabbhāre. "
msgstr "At one time the venerables Sāriputta and Upasena were staying near Rājagaha in the Cool Wood, under the Snake’s Hood Grotto. "

msgctxt "sn35.69:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmato upasenassa kāye āsīviso patito hoti. "
msgstr "Now at that time a viper fell on Upasena’s body, "

msgctxt "sn35.69:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā upaseno bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "and he addressed the mendicants, "

msgctxt "sn35.69:1.4"
msgid "“etha me, āvuso, imaṃ kāyaṃ mañcakaṃ āropetvā bahiddhā nīharatha. "
msgstr "“Come, reverends, lift this body onto a cot and carry it outside "

msgctxt "sn35.69:1.5"
msgid "Purāyaṃ kāyo idheva vikirati; "
msgstr "before it’s scattered right here "

msgctxt "sn35.69:1.6"
msgid "seyyathāpi bhusamuṭṭhī”ti. "
msgstr "like a handful of chaff.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.41, sc2
msgctxt "sn35.69:2.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, āyasmā sāriputto āyasmantaṃ upasenaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When he said this, Sāriputta said to him, "

msgctxt "sn35.69:2.2"
msgid "“na kho pana mayaṃ passāma āyasmato upasenassa kāyassa vā aññathattaṃ indriyānaṃ vā vipariṇāmaṃ. "
msgstr "“But we don’t see any impairment in your body or deterioration of your faculties. "

msgctxt "sn35.69:2.3"
msgid "Atha ca panāyasmā upaseno evamāha: "
msgstr "Yet you say: "

msgctxt "sn35.69:2.4"
msgid "‘etha me, āvuso, imaṃ kāyaṃ mañcakaṃ āropetvā bahiddhā nīharatha. "
msgstr "‘Come, reverends, lift this body onto a cot and carry it outside "

msgctxt "sn35.69:2.5"
msgid "Purāyaṃ kāyo idheva vikirati; "
msgstr "before it’s scattered right here "

msgctxt "sn35.69:2.6"
msgid "seyyathāpi bhusamuṭṭhī’”ti. "
msgstr "like a handful of chaff.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.69:2.7"
msgid "“Yassa nūna, āvuso sāriputta, evamassa: "
msgstr "“Reverend Sāriputta, there may be an impairment in body or deterioration of faculties for someone who thinks: "

msgctxt "sn35.69:2.8"
msgid "‘ahaṃ cakkhūti vā mama cakkhūti vā … pe … "
msgstr "‘I am the eye’ or ‘the eye is mine.’ "

msgctxt "sn35.69:2.9"
msgid "ahaṃ jivhāti vā mama jivhāti vā … "
msgstr "Or ‘I am the ear … nose … tongue … body …’ "

msgctxt "sn35.69:2.10"
msgid "ahaṃ manoti vā mama mano’ti vā. "
msgstr "Or ‘I am the mind’ or ‘the mind is mine.’ "

msgctxt "sn35.69:2.11"
msgid "Tassa, āvuso sāriputta, siyā kāyassa vā aññathattaṃ indriyānaṃ vā vipariṇāmo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.69:2.12"
msgid "Mayhañca kho, āvuso sāriputta, na evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "But I don’t think like that. "

msgctxt "sn35.69:2.13"
msgid "‘ahaṃ cakkhūti vā mama cakkhūti vā … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.69:2.14"
msgid "ahaṃ jivhāti vā mama jivhāti vā … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.69:2.15"
msgid "ahaṃ manoti vā mama manoti vā’. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.69:2.16"
msgid "Tassa mayhañca kho, āvuso sāriputta, kiṃ kāyassa vā aññathattaṃ bhavissati, indriyānaṃ vā vipariṇāmo”ti. "
msgstr "So why would there be an impairment in my body or deterioration of my faculties?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
#. VAR: ahaṅkāramamaṅkāramānānusayo susamūhato → … mānānusayā susamūhatā (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.69:3.1"
msgid "Tathā hi panāyasmato upasenassa dīgharattaṃ ahaṅkāramamaṅkāramānānusayo susamūhato. "
msgstr "“That must be because Venerable Upasena has long ago totally eradicated ego, possessiveness, and the underlying tendency to conceit. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.69:3.2"
msgid "Tasmā āyasmato upasenassa na evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "That’s why it doesn’t occur to you: "

msgctxt "sn35.69:3.3"
msgid "“‘ahaṃ cakkhūti vā mama cakkhūti vā … pe … "
msgstr "‘I am the eye’ or ‘the eye is mine.’ Or ‘I am the ear … "

msgctxt "sn35.69:3.4"
msgid "ahaṃ jivhāti vā mama jivhāti vā … pe … "
msgstr "nose … tongue … body …’ "

msgctxt "sn35.69:3.5"
msgid "ahaṃ manoti vā mama mano’ti vā”ti. "
msgstr "Or ‘I am the mind’ or ‘the mind is mine.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.69:3.6"
msgid "Atha kho te bhikkhū āyasmato upasenassa kāyaṃ mañcakaṃ āropetvā bahiddhā nīhariṃsu. "
msgstr "Then those mendicants lifted Upasena’s body onto a cot and carried it outside. "

msgctxt "sn35.69:3.7"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmato upasenassa kāyo tattheva vikiri; "
msgstr "And his body was scattered right there "

msgctxt "sn35.69:3.8"
msgid "seyyathāpi bhusamuṭṭhīti. "
msgstr "like a handful of chaff. "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.69:3.9"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

